[Installing jlibcpp]

:Dependencies

- openssl (http://www.openssl.org)

[directfb]
- directfb (http://directfb.org)

[directfb, directfb-cairo]
- directfb (http://directfb.org)
- cairo (http://cairographics.org)

[gtk3]
- gtk+ (http://www.gtk.org/)

[sdl2]
- sdl2 (https://www.libsdl.org)
- libsdl2_ttf (https://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf)
- libsdl2_image (https://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image)

:Makefile defines

ENABLE_DEBUG=<no, yes>
ENABLE_GRAPHICS=<none, directfb, directfb-cairo, gtk3, sdl2>

:Compiling

$ export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=<pkg-path>
$ sudo make all install

[Compilling tests]

For each module of jlibcpp, change to tests directory and type:

"make"

[Compiling applications]

## Makefile -- with pkgconfig -- begin ##

CFLAGS	= `pkg-config --cflags jlibcpp`
LIBS		= `pkg-config --libs jlibcpp`

all:
	g++ <app.cpp> -o <app> $(CFLAGS) $(LIBS)

## Makefile -- with pkgconfig -- end ##

